---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials & Reviews for Gyms — SocialProof" description="Collect member testimonials and display them on your gym website. Works with any site builder. Free to start, $9/month Pro. No code required." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/gyms">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: 0.45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .for-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0fdf4; color: #16a34a; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .pain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .pain-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.25rem; }
    .pain-card .icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
    .pain-card h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 0.97rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .pain-card p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .steps { counter-reset: step; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .steps li { counter-increment: step; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .steps li::before { content: counter(step); min-width: 2rem; height: 2rem; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
    .steps li .step-text h3 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .steps li .step-text p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .testimonial-example { background: #f8f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; margin: 2rem 0; font-size: 1rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; }
    .testimonial-example cite { display: block; margin-top: .75rem; font-style: normal; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #888; }
    .timing-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1.5px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .timing-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .75rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #92400e; }
    .timing-box ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; color: #555; font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.85; }
    .platform-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    .platform-pill { background: #f3f4f6; border-radius: 99px; padding: .4rem 1rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: #374151; font-weight: 500; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .cta-section h2 { color: #fff; }
    .cta-section p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-section a { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 .75rem; }
</style>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for/">Who it's for</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/app/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="for-badge">💪 For Gyms & Fitness Centers</div>
  <h1>Your members get<br/><span>real results.</span><br/>Show them off.</h1>
  <p>Before someone buys a membership, they want to know it works. SocialProof helps gyms collect text testimonials from members and display them on your website — automatically, with no tech skills needed.</p>
  <a href="/app/signup" class="hero-cta">Start collecting testimonials free</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Why gym owners struggle with testimonials</h2>
  <div class="pain-grid">
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="icon">😬</div>
      <h3>Asking feels awkward</h3>
      <p>Pulling a member aside mid-workout to ask for a review is uncomfortable for both of you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="icon">⭐</div>
      <h3>Google reviews go to Google</h3>
      <p>When members leave reviews, they go to Google — not to the page where your next prospect is deciding to buy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="icon">📸</div>
      <h3>Before/after is complicated</h3>
      <p>Not every member wants photos shared. A written testimonial respects privacy and still converts visitors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-card">
      <div class="icon">🔧</div>
      <h3>Tech is a barrier</h3>
      <p>Most gym owners don't have time to learn a new platform. You need something that works in minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:#f9f9f9; padding: 3rem 2rem;">
  <div style="max-width:900px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>How SocialProof works for gyms</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Sign up and get your collection link</h3>
          <p>Takes 2 minutes. No credit card required. Your link is ready immediately — share it with members via text, email, or a QR code at the front desk.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Members type their testimonial — no app download</h3>
          <p>They click the link, type what they'd like to say, and submit. Works on any phone. Takes under a minute.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>You approve and display it</h3>
          <p>Review every testimonial before it goes live. Approve the good ones, skip anything vague. Your website only shows what you choose.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Paste the widget on your gym's website</h3>
          <p>Copy one line of code. Works on Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Webflow, or any site with an HTML embed option.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>When to ask for a testimonial</h2>
  <div class="timing-box">
    <h3>🎯 Best moments to send your collection link</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>After a member hits a milestone — first 5kg lost, first pull-up, first 5K</li>
      <li>At the end of a challenge or 6-week program</li>
      <li>After a member renews their membership or upgrades</li>
      <li>When a member thanks you in person — "Mind if I send you a link to write that down?"</li>
      <li>30 days into a new membership, once they've seen real progress</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="testimonial-example">
    "I'd tried three other gyms in the area and never stuck with it. The coaching here is different — trainers actually check in on you. I've lost 12kg in four months and I look forward to coming in."
    <cite>— Sarah K., member since 2024</cite>
  </div>
  <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.92rem;">That kind of testimonial converts new membership inquiries. It's specific, it's credible, and it addresses the exact objection ("will I actually stick with it?") that holds people back.</p>
</section>

<section style="background:#f9f9f9; padding: 3rem 2rem;">
  <div style="max-width:900px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h2>Works with your existing website</h2>
    <p style="color:#555; margin-bottom:1rem;">SocialProof embeds work on every major site builder. You don't need to rebuild your website.</p>
    <div class="platform-list">
      <span class="platform-pill">Squarespace</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">Wix</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">WordPress</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">Webflow</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">GoDaddy Website Builder</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">Showit</span>
      <span class="platform-pill">Custom HTML</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Related: other fitness businesses using SocialProof</h2>
  <p style="color:#555;">SocialProof works across the fitness industry. See how similar businesses use it:</p>
  <ul style="color:#4f46e5; line-height:2; padding-left:1.5rem;">
    <li><a href="/for/yoga-studios" style="color:#4f46e5;">Yoga studios</a></li>
    <li><a href="/for/fitness-studios" style="color:#4f46e5;">Fitness studios</a></li>
    <li><a href="/for/personal-trainers" style="color:#4f46e5;">Personal trainers</a></li>
  </ul>
</section>

<div class="cta-section">
  <h2>Start collecting gym testimonials today.</h2>
  <p>Free forever for 1 widget. No credit card. No code needed.</p>
  <a href="/app/signup">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <a href="/">SocialProof</a>
  <a href="/for/">Who it's for</a>
  <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
  <a href="/app/signup">Sign up free</a>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
